<%- include('partials/head', { title: 'FAQs | Cleanny' }) %>
<section class="section">
  <div class="wrap narrow">
    <p class="eyebrow">FAQs</p>
    <h1>Frequently asked questions</h1>
    <details open><summary>How do I book a clean with Cleanny?</summary><p>Choose your service, pick a date and time slot, add your address and confirm. You'll get an instant booking reference and email confirmation.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Can I reschedule or cancel?</summary><p>Yes — free of charge up to 24 hours before your slot. Within 24 hours a small late-change fee may apply.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Do I need to provide products or equipment?</summary><p>No. Your Cleanny professional brings everything needed, including eco-friendly products on request.</p></details>
    <details><summary>Are your cleaners vetted?</summary><p>Every professional is identity-verified, background-checked and continuously review-monitored.</p></details>
    <details><summary>How do payments work?</summary><p>No payment is taken at booking. You pay after the clean by card or bank transfer, and receive an invoice by email.</p></details>
    <details><summary>What if I'm not happy with the clean?</summary><p>Tell us within 48 hours and we'll return to re-clean the affected areas free of charge.</p></details>
  </div>
</section>
<%- include('partials/foot') %>

